headline: Welcome, Luxembourg City and Chișinău! Cloudflare Global Network Spans 151 Cities
keywords: March of Cloudflare, Europe, Data Center, Cloudflare Network
description: Hot off the presses! Cloudflare just completed provisioning our Luxembourg and Chișinău data centers, expanding our Europe network to 41 cities, and our global network to 151 cities across 74 countries.
